snippet.title: GoGoKid and VIPKID Taxes | An Interview with a Tax Professional
snippet.description:
It's time for Taxes 101! Your first year doing taxes as a VIPKID teacher can be so stressful. Amber is a tax professional who is also a VIPKID teacher and she has been a resource to SO MANY teachers. I hope this interview with a tax professional can help you with GoGoKid or VIPKID taxes. My FREE taxes guide can be found here: https://www.cookfamilyresources.com/how-to-treat-your-online-esl-business-as-a-business/

Check out Amber's Website to connect with her. She offers complete Federal and State tax returns starting at $70.
https://www.taxintegrity.org/

Learn about estimated payments
https://www.irs.gov/payments

Get your expenses organized
https://storage.googleapis.com/wzukusers/user-34713868/documents/b8440e6eef81480d8c4b851e9dbef0f2/Online%20Teaching%20Deduction%20Worksheet.pdf

Learn more about that Home Office Deduction
https://www.irs.gov/businesses/small-businesses-self-employed/home-office-deduction
